    "Several measurements are adopted.",
    "These measurements are accuracy, specificity, sensitivity, F1-score, receiver operating characteristic (ROC) curve, and convergence curve.",
    "These measurements provide information about several elements of the model's performance.",
    "Specificity assesses the model's ability to correctly identify instances that do not belong to a certain class.",
    "It represents the proportion of true negative instances to the overall number of negative instances."
  ],
